│ predicate, adds it as a fact to Info, and if that implies the compare being   │
│ simplified, it replaces the operand with a constant.\n\n3. Root Cause         │
│ Analysis:\ncheckOrAndOpImpliedByOther is designed to simplify AND/OR trees by │
